{"type": "article", "id": 19694, "title": "可移动的沙发组", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-25T07:00:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021108201IHGpt5YQNrvliUx.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦设计工作室 Kilo Design 为家具品牌 +Halle 设计了一组可移动的沙发，三个为一组。一块长条状的沙发横放在两个的中间，有一张桌子的高度，也可以当做靠背。它还可以随意移动，划分出一个讨论区，很适合放在图书馆等公共环境中。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150142d6eTEkoj2AW7Vanw.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"573\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61217949\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150143Pj7Lf1J0mnhoxST3.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150144Uc45WhNrbItF27DY.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"1403\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49893162\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150145czu840x7MlsIpt63.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"1403\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49893162\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}